            <section class="home" id="home">
                <div class="home__container container grid">
                    <img src="https://p-news-upload.storage.googleapis.com/2023/02/Julian-van-Dieken_A-Girl-With-Glowing-Earrings-.png" alt="AI Robot" class="home__img">
            
                    <div class="home__data">
                        <h1 class="home__title">
                            What is Artificial Intelligence (AI)?
                        </h1>
                        <p class="home__description">
                            Artificial Intelligence, or AI, refers to computer systems designed to perform tasks that normally require human intelligence. These tasks can include recognizing speech, making decisions, translating languages, and solving problems. AI systems learn from data, adapt to new situations, and improve their performance over time. In simple terms, AI is like giving machines the ability to think and learn like humans do.
                        </p>
                        <a href="index.html" class="button button--flex">
                            Back Home <i class="ri-arrow-right-down-line button__icon"></i>
                        </a>
                    </div>
