            <section class="about section container" id="about">
                <div class="about__container grid">
                    <img src="https://images.nightcafe.studio/jobs/Mjp8b5tA9rla5iwaA8TP/Mjp8b5tA9rla5iwaA8TP--1--y72eg_7.8125x.jpg?tr=w-1600,c-at_max" alt="AI in Action" class="about__img">
            
                    <div class="about__data">
                        <h2 class="section__title about__title">
                            How Does AI Work?
                        </h2>
            
                        <p class="about__description">
                            AI works by using algorithms, which are sets of rules or instructions, to process and analyze large amounts of data. These algorithms can recognize patterns, make predictions, and learn from experiences. AI systems are trained on data sets, and as they process more data, they get better at performing their tasks. For example, an AI trained on many pictures of cats can learn to identify a cat in a new photo.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            
            <section class="home" id="home">
                <div class="home__container container grid">
                    <img src="https://images.nightcafe.studio/jobs/0bfKcQoSQxFuAg9s7B1d/0bfKcQoSQxFuAg9s7B1d--1--0ao0t.jpg?tr=w-1600,c-at_max" alt="AI Benefits" class="home__img">
            
                    <div class="home__data">
                        <h1 class="section__title about__title">
                            What Are the Benefits of AI?
                        </h1>
                        <br>
                        <p class="home__description">
                            AI offers many benefits by making processes more efficient and accurate. It can handle repetitive tasks quickly, analyze vast amounts of data, and provide insights that might be missed by humans. For example, AI helps in diagnosing diseases, automating factory work, and personalizing recommendations on streaming services. Overall, AI can save time, reduce errors, and make complex tasks easier to manage.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            
            <section class="about section container" id="about">
                <div class="about__container grid">
                    <img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1024/1*qZOadooIoRfBMkWYBUfk-A.png" alt="AI Applications" class="about__img">
            
                    <div class="about__data">
                        <h2 class="section__title about__title">
                            How Is AI Used in Everyday Life?
                        </h2>
            
                        <p class="about__description">
                            AI is used in many ways in our daily lives. For instance, virtual assistants like Siri and Alexa use AI to understand and respond to our questions. AI also powers recommendation systems on platforms like Netflix and Amazon, helping you discover new movies or products based on your interests. In healthcare, AI assists doctors by analyzing medical images and suggesting treatments. In short, AI is embedded in many technologies we use every day, making them smarter and more helpful.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
